        <mxCell id="footnotes" value="[1] VIPs are free IPs on the same L2 subnet as the nodes, managed by keepalived (not assigned to any host).&#10;[2] VLAN is optional. Set vlan=100 in cluster.conf. Without it, nodes use untagged frames on the host network.&#10;[3] Bond is optional. List multiple interfaces in cluster.conf ports= (e.g. ports=ens1f0,ens2f0) to enable bonding." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=9;fontColor=#555555;fontFamily=Red Hat Display;spacingLeft=4;" vertex="1" parent="1">
